a:xfrm><a:off x="4636757" y="1674643"/><a:ext cx="7327688" cy="4154984"/></a:xfrm><a:prstGeom prst="rect"><a:avLst/></a:prstGeom><a:noFill/></p:spPr><p:txBody><a:bodyPr wrap="square"><a:spAutoFit/></a:bodyPr><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:pPr><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/><a:t>Makeko Interiors was founded by Mosa Dineo Makgoka, a qualified interior designer with more than 10 years of experience in the design industry.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/><a:t>She obtained her Interior Design qualification from Inscape Education Group in 2014 and is currently pursuing a Postgraduate qualification in Interior Design at the University of Johannesburg.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/></a:p><a:p><a:pPr><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/><a:t>Her professional experience includes projects in several sectors:</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/><a:t>• Healthcare Facilities</a:t></a:r><a:br><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/></a:br><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/><a:t>• Corporate Office Environments</a:t></a:r><a:br><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/></a:br><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/><a:t>• Retail Spaces</a:t></a:r><a:br><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/></a:br><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/><a:t>• Residential Interiors</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/></a:p><a:p><a:pPr><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/><a:t>With strong expertise in technical interior design documentation and detailing, Mosa brings a structured and disciplined approach to design development while maintaining a passion for creativity and innovation.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/></a:p><a:p><a:pPr><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/><a:t>Her design philosophy focuses on creating spaces that are:</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/></a:p><a:p><a:pPr><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/><a:t>• Functional</a:t></a:r><a:br><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/></a:br><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/><a:t>• Efficient</a:t></a:r><a:br><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/></a:br><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/><a:t>• Emotionally engaging</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/></a:p><a:p><a:pPr><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"/><a:t>while ensuring that every design solution is supported by strong technical documentation and industry standards.</a:t></a:r></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp></p:spTree><p:extLst><p:ext uri="{BB962C8B-B14F-4D97-AF65-F5344CB8AC3E}"><p14:creationId xmlns:p14="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/powerpoint/2010/main" val="2062313232"/></p:ext></p:extLst></p:cSld><p:clrMapOvr><a:masterClrMapping/></p:clrMapOvr></p:sld>